<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Página no encontrada - NovaCare</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">
    
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/img/logo_removed.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="assets/img/logo_removed.png">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="assets/img/logo_removed.png" type="image/x-icon">
    
    <style>
        .gradient-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f7ff 0%, #ffffff 100%); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="font-sans text-slate-800 antialiased overflow-x-hidden bg-white flex flex-col min-h-screen">

    <div id="header-placeholder"></div>

    <main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center gradient-bg pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center" data-aos="zoom-in">
            
            <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-8">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-100 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-50"></div>
                <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-full h-full bg-white rounded-full shadow-lg text-blue-500 text-5xl">
                    <i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-400 mb-4">
                404
            </h1>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">
                ¡Página no encontrada!
            </h2>
            
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed px-4">
                Parece que te has perdido. La página que buscas no existe, ha cambiado de nombre o está temporalmente inaccesible. ¡Permítenos guiarte de vuelta a la salud!
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="./index.html" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-200 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i> Volver al Inicio
                </a>
                <a href="./contacto.html" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white border-2 border-blue-100 text-blue-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:border-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all">
                    <i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i> Contactar Soporte
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <div id="footer-placeholder"></div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    
    <script src="assets/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>